site_name:
Bankside Industrial Estate 
118 Southwark Street And 
44 Holland Street And 47 Hopton Street
London 
SE1 OSW
description: Alterations during the course of construction of approved scheme granted permission on 19.6.07 with ref: 06/AP/1481 (for the demolition of existing buildings and the erection of five buildings, one six storey, two 12 storey, one 18 storey and one 24 storey, each with two basement levels to provide 229 residential units on the upper floors, with retail Class A1, A2 and A3 use at the ground floor with landscaping and other ancillary works) relating to alterations to the mix of residential units including an increase in the number of units by 4 (no increase in floorspace is proposed), to a total of 233 units.
